feat: Implement book update form with real-time validation

- Added a full HTML form for updating book details, including inputs for title, author, price, quantity, description, category, and image uploads
- Integrated existing book data into form fields for pre-filled values
- Assigned unique IDs to each input for easy DOM targeting
- Implemented real-time front-end validation using JavaScript for all form fields:
  - Title length check
  - Author name format validation
  - Numeric and range checks for price and quantity
  - Description length enforcement
  - File extension validation for uploaded images
- Displayed inline validation messages under each input field
- Ensured form submission is blocked until all fields are valid




